headline: Franklin Templeton Canada Expands ETF Platform with Launch of Franklin U.S. Quality Moat Dividend Index ETF and the Franklin FTSE India Index ETF
summary: Franklin Templeton Canada today announced the expansion of its ETF platform to include two new index-tracking ETFs: the Franklin U.S. Quality Moat Dividend Index ETF [ticker: FDIV] and the Franklin FTSE India Index ETF [ticker: FID] with an industry low-management fee.
